WEBVTT

00:03.071 --> 00:05.342
April 22nd is Earth Day,...

00:08.584 --> 00:12.995
...a celebration of our fragile environment and of our efforts to preserve it.

00:15.113 --> 00:18.853
This Earth Day also marks the signing of the landmark Paris agreement.

00:21.195 --> 00:24.013
This is a United Nations agreement that sets targets...

00:24.093 --> 00:26.055
...for reduced greenhouse gas emissions...

00:26.701 --> 00:28.405
...aimed at holding the warming of the planet...

00:28.978 --> 00:32.430
...at less than two degrees Celsius above its pre-industrial level.

00:34.891 --> 00:37.995
It also lays out ways in which finance can be used...

00:38.076 --> 00:41.695
...to guide signatories towards a low-emission future.

00:49.838 --> 00:53.275
Some 120 countries are expected to sign the agreement today...

00:54.903 --> 00:56.769
...including the US and China,...

00:57.999 --> 01:01.089
...providing hope for the future of our world.

